name: Strathcona County Open Data
description: Strathcona County is committed to being an open and transparent government. Data is available license free, in a digital format, to be used by the public to analyze, download or connect to data sets creating applications and services for the benefit of all members of the County. The catalogue includes data such as civic address, contours, neighbourhoods, orthophotos, storm, street network, water, waste water and much more.
